===Noun Phrase===
'''immune system'''

# {{anatomy}} The system that differentiates self from nonself and protects the body from foreign substances and pathogenic organisms by producing an [[immune response]]. It includes organs such as the [[thymus]], the [[spleen]] and [[lymph node]]s; tissue such as [[bone marrow]], and lymphoid tissues such as the [[tonsil]]s; cells such as  [[lymphocyte]]s including the [[B cell]]s and [[T cell]]s, and cell products such as [[antibody|antibodies]].

